&lt;p&gt;This is a &quot;bilingual&quot; People Partnership role. You must be as comfortable partnering with senior leaders to develop scalable change strategies, proactively planning for contingencies and championing the vision through effective storytelling, as you are walking the floor of a robust call center to understand engagement drivers.&lt;/p&gt;
