&lt;li&gt;Anticipate challenges and opportunities by helping leaders ‘see around corners’, offering proactive guidance and insights that inform smarter organizational and talent decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach and empower leaders by providing guidance on leadership challenges, performance management, team dynamics, and navigating complex people challenges across the employee lifecycle.&lt;/li&gt;
