&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical and People Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Guide the team in building scalable, cloud-native backend services and integrations using our tech stack (Java/Spring Cloud, Kafka, AWS, Kubernetes, PostgreSQL) and Business Rules Management Systems (BRMS).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
